  "title": "And you thought there is never a girl online?",
  "synopsis": "The story centers on Hideki Nishimura, a young man who confessed to a person he thought was a girl online, only for that person to turn out to be a boy. He keeps this \"black history\" secret and swears to never to trust a \"girl\" online again. However, one day a girl online confesses to him, and it turns out she's actually a beautiful girl named Ako Tamaki. Ako cannot tell the difference between the online world and reality, and she is a loner who has trouble communicating. Hideki and his friends from his guild decide to work together to \"correct\" her.\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)",
